{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM6nOlVFgMKicVRUia54mssmloGh0KvYD5Y5lt4wibRMMsZtUPpl2qCFFP8Htv3xUYf2kcUupGe8gjVqg/0","content":"<p>客户关系维护的途径（按使用频率排序）：</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px;\">微信、</span>邮件、电话、面对面沟通、视频、吃饭喝茶</p><p>我认为以上途径都是有效的，只是效果有先后排名，如下：</p><p>有效方案：面对面沟通、吃饭喝茶、电话、视频、微信、邮件</p><p>个人感觉，有直观的视觉或声音的沟通能较好地维护客户关系，当然，人与人之间的关系也如此。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8524,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492679900000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Grace谷","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icye0y15ytCp7Be1mStPR9VjXsjtBDNWKpmdicgcr7efY9cKpcJmqb7n6x2pkKviaE67VjB35fgjR4Q/0","content":"我的客户主要是国外贸易公司或者供应商：<div>1、关注各国节日和客户生日，即使通过邮件或者社交软件（WhatsApp &nbsp;Facebook)等发送祝福。</div><div>2、适时将我司重要积极的动态新闻分享给客户，增强客户对我们的信任。</div><div>3、关注客户国家市场新闻动态，作为交流的话题。</div><div>4、参加各国展会的时候带上具有中国特色的礼品，送给客户，增进感情。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8487,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492674763000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8hWCY4rsU5ic7YX8NSbKTQ1jqib9icr5cJBexUUicYhHibyRcicc1Y9Hxmc5hFqdxgaUNjiaBH4HIahUdE/0","content":"<p>维持现有关系：</p><p>1、 外部客户：工作邮件/电话交流/与客户当面技术交流/微信建立私人关系（有效）</p><p>2、 内部客户：工作汇报（有效）</p><p>创造新客户关系：</p><p>1、 给新客户提供技术方案（有效）</p><p>2、参加行业协会，谋求建立新的客户关系（有效）<br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7953,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492502644000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"<p><img alt=\"屏幕快照 2017-04-17 下午3.00.56.png\" style=\"max-width:90%\" src=\"http://static.iqycamp.com/application-20170417150105-v8fabk29a.png\"><br></p><p>这些都是一般的途径，我现在需要做的是，更深入地了解客户对这些途径的偏好，从而更有针对性地发挥这些途径的作用。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7856,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492412513000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"貓宁姜","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6agqPwVy4opWYcSWZaVneib0f1rTHkIZ5qhFcGKRAEsbjrQibqJfRIenSXe22uFMgHC2O99xEGECEh6e11rMFfjO9/0","content":"<p>维护关系的途径：定期汇报，日报、周报</p><p>有效方案：定期汇报</p><p>无效方案：抱怨</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7680,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492131362000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Elva","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoFaxYzCOkAgT6U2G0vGpXUa0F8N8eibrdQDFDpDsIQR0o4LFlkibaV2e9sqVQWTSnESkEN3QcQNcXz/0","content":"1. 领导： &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 邮件和口头形式汇报和讨论相关的问题。有些未及时沟通，造成双方的误解。<div>2. &nbsp;销售人员 &nbsp; &nbsp; 跟进他们的问题，发邮件尽量简明扼要，节省时间，提高效率。</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6039,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491556090000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"\uD83D\uDC8DEileen\uD83D\uDD06","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6abalthMJiaYnoibZVuO5CvSR8HOKWNjhJyafcnkmAkvTZ9NZIu7ibtL0hZb0tFft1ZWlJB8cmhjzGuaQSxNldicib3T/0","content":"<div>主要面对公司内部群体</div><div>领导</div>微信，qq和面对面交流<div>以后多注重面对面沟通</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7142,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491222093000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lanlan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoABxary8VgXcewR1AmF19vgqh1yjicvfMjehwnN9BCtpicJfHXYmt3tEsP23v1u2lfVGIFicncrooia2/0","content":"客户关系\n\n1、团队负责人\n\n   这方面主要有两个途径。（1）向团队负责人提交项目方案并讨论，这个途径比较有效，但是由于团队负责人口头表达能力比较强，又比较喜欢把控讨论的主动权，所以在讨论之前需要做好充分准备，讨论中以简洁的语言直接抛出自己的观点，并阐述理由，这样才能说服对方。（2）定期向团队负责人汇报工作情况，由于团队负责人比较雷厉风行，对项目有严格的时间限要求，因此定期向其汇报进展情况非常有必要，需要让他了解已经解决了哪些问题，还需要进行哪些方面的协调，这样也有助于获得对方的帮助，因此，这种途径同样有效。\n\n   而这方面的无效途径可能包括向团队负责人抱怨项目资源的缺乏等等，因为无谓的抱怨解决不了问题，只会对团队带来负面影响，不利于团队团结，因此团队负责人对此必定是反感的。\n\n2、客户\n   这方面主要包括三个途径：（1）与客户定期沟通了解他们的新需求和遇到的难题，途径有效，一方面让客户知道我们对该领域的持续关注，另一方面也及时调整发展方向；\n（2）按照客户需求进行产品完善和维护，途径有效。客户所需要的是稳定可靠的产品和不断满足其需求变化的产品；（3）团队与客户吃饭沟通，通过这种非工作性的交流，及时沟通感情，建立起稳固的合作关系。\n\n    综上所述，通过将有效与无效方案的归类，我觉得维护客户关系的途径应该根据客户的特点和喜好来选择有效的方式。简单的说就是，你的老板如果喜欢口头汇报，那么你应该采用简短精炼的语言表达出你的观点；如果你的老板喜欢看书面报告，那么你应该提高自己的写作能力，定期给他提供工作汇报。\n <img src=\"http://www.iqycamp.com/images/application/application-20170330205405-02a7mpv4r-6467.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:90%\"/>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6467,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490972456000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":["http://www.iqycamp.com/images/application/application-20170330205405-02a7mpv4r-6467.jpeg"]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"日常沟通、拜访的面对面交流\n社交软件互动\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6876,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490922025000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"影子（one life one liver）","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-28","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay7P6qrmu6EFgMxv9yByicqqSVMrdaJoMs4TEyich23rD3ictMbhBfngbwia0x0G3qzXEM5ib5SQ8bx5vQ/0","content":"外部客户：客户病人，内部客户：科室同事,辅助科室。\n维护关系方式1.提高服务态度，让诊疗工作变得美好，使用吸引力法则，方式每日精进+复利。2.重复性事务流程化，多出来的时间用于沟通，学习，思考，提高业务水准。3.和内部客户加强协调同，优化工作流程，加强有效沟通，利用合作请教的机会，加深内部客户的联系和感情。\n曾经使用的无效方案：1.延长工作时间。2.沟通重形式轻效果。3.提升自我的目标不明确，笼统含混，使得陷入低水平勤奋的自嗨状态。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6380,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490712983000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lasia","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-27","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQPZjdCpPKAMDUgWoXUvkVcsqzWKUUicQdLDqSSXIAzKphVGZMibQL8RZHItR7wlTetH47SYQgiasgxu/0","content":"<p>1.对于供应商、货代和国外客户，由于地域问题，采用邮件、qq、电话的方式，进行维护和合作。</p><p>2.对于上司，多采用面对面交流的方式进行维护和合作，另也采用qq和电话沟通的方式。</p><p>主要表现为：积极完成分发的任务；有问题时，及时核对问题、向他讲述我的解决思路和方案，若是不知如何处理的便直接寻求帮助。</p><p>这些都属于有效方式，但有时候一种方式会行不通，立马换另外一种方式沟通。开发新客户都是上司在开发。</p><p>以前，也会有一起吃饭的维护关系，但后来由于某些不好的原因，加上我工种的原因，线下维护方式不太必要，于是我就中止了这种方式。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4430,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490608621000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寒子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-26","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay51LC8HCDuYJSWhCiaGfzmy3VbcicUnvJZlFqenDgwRweEhJT3NUuHcdKOrfibQdiaxPrT2cZX8r6hsT/0","content":"维护现有客户：\n外部：对患者家属-耐心沟通病情，建立信任感\n内部：\n带组教授-管理共同病人，一起吃饭\n年轻医师-指导业务，一起吃饭\n科主任-做好现有工作\n\n扩大客户关系：暂无\n\n有效途径：以上途径其实都算有效，只不过大部分都是通过日常工作建立的关系，尤其在扩大客户关系上没有帮助，究其原因还是在自我品牌的建立上疏于管理。\n\n改进方式：\n外部：1.更多站在患者角度考虑问题，与患者建立更深层次互相信任的联系2.增加自己在相关医疗网站的曝光和宣传3.建立患者线上群\n内部：1.增加线上课程，辐射更多地区年轻医生2.提升科研能力，更得到领导的支持\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4604,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490459045000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jill Ling","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-25","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyyZN53g2CvLEGicxZ4heLHooiaCVwibvbcw8BcDsxgL2AMj3bgU2wNX8OPexCoDeHxKxE9KicExhXd1G/0","content":"已经在做：\n1.与内部用户聊天以了解使用习惯和服务问题\n2.参加各种公司内部活动以拉近与用户关系\n3.通过服务满意度调查了解用户反馈\n\n应该要做\n1）与部门关键用户紧密联系，了解业务部门动态\n2）与部门经理和主管多互动，了解部门需求\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5657,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490451415000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"俞悦","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-25","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLANZo09gQTTkSzvHFqibxNaah02fZMYxmspFkicQSzo8hbBVImPBFbjOkYibjAmt9lUUMaJHNB54hAWw/0","content":"低成本维系，邮件微信QQ以及电话联系，工作往来\n\n\n高成本维系，面谈拜访，吃饭娱乐，优质服务\n\n\n最有效的是优质服务，需要花更多精力和心思在这方面，难点痛点也在这。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5529,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490435410000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JO","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","content":"建立与客户的有效交流和情感联系，通过微信、邮件、电话等方式维护客户关系。有较深入的问题，当面商讨会比较高效。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5096,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490226175000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"1.老板\n①接到任务时花更多时间在澄清问题的沟通上，避免因为误会而出现分歧；\n②从老板的角度去思考政策的实施，同理心待之；\n\n2.家长\n①更多地关注孩子能力提升方面，给予家庭策略；\n②积极增加沟通，提升沟通质量，协助排除障碍和问题；\n\n3.孩子\n①设计更有趣味性的课程，加强上课兴趣和意愿；\n②关注上课时孩子的情绪变化，心理状态，及时疏导和干预；","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4480,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490005302000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"茜子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJ58zzeAvjk9egsh7pI0xaJnzicWDeplo17IiaNXickic8DF3Zlst8Q0iapLbQtCHZvpOerIF8aXibO6obBD9TuUW7KAq/0","content":"内部客户维持途径：\n高质量完成任务在上司面前博得好感\n有困难的时候向上司寻求帮助，说说自己的想法，促进沟通。\n\n外部客户维持途径：\n学生：通过上课批改作业，班会，课下交流，课外活动维持。\n\n家长：通过微信群等让他们及时了解现阶段学生的情况，学校有什么改变，是为了什么，寻求在为了孩子发展的共同目标下，家长可以配合我的工作。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4160,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489888556000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Elaine","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcIfBefSOI7eDbibj4dAR87Cqia4x8KPur35Lmle8oSKpoJOSbGBDL2KIhWIQytUkBKO4goVoXLbUTxbc2pibVSwZ9b/0","content":"工作日每日邮件汇总报告\n电话答疑","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3980,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489811617000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
